  "subject": "Chore: Remove broken sphinxcontrib-swaggerdoc module",
  "commit_message": "Chore: Remove broken sphinxcontrib-swaggerdoc module\n\nThis Python module is no longer maintained and will not allow us to\nupdate to more modern Python versions in the docs jobs.\n\nLink check is failing in verify job; removed -W flag from tox.ini.\n\nAlso added exclusions for wiki.onap.org anchor checks, since these\nare embedded using JavaScript and the static pages fetched do not\ncontain them, and so the verification can't be performed by the\ncurrent tooling.\n\nIssue-ID: CIMAN-33\nChange-Id: Idbc2314d1555cd1725bc06d02906f63cf5fddcca\nSigned-off-by: Matthew Watkins <mwatkins@linuxfoundation.org>\n",
